# S03-T03: Telemetry Widgets

## Objective
Port battery + connection status widgets, plus add ALT/SPD/SIG/BAT compact tiles.

## Acceptance Criteria
- `src/features/hud/widgets/BatteryWidget.tsx` shows cell levels, charge state, voltage.
- `src/features/hud/widgets/SignalWidget.tsx` shows link quality bars, SIG dB.
- `src/features/hud/widgets/TelemetryTile.tsx` reusable tile (label + value + unit).
- Low battery / poor signal triggers pink alert color + 1Hz pulse animation.

## Steps
1. Build `<TelemetryTile>` (label, value, unit, severity).
2. Build `<BatteryWidget>` composed of cell segments.
3. Build `<SignalWidget>` (5 bars + numeric dB).
4. Bind all to `useTelemetryStore`.

## Invariants
- UPPERCASE abbreviated labels (ALT, SPD, SIG, BAT) per UI_REGULATION.
- Pulse animation: opacity-only, 1Hz, no scale/translate.
- Severity colors mapped to UI_REGULATION palette.
